                  ʾAbbā
               </foaf:name><crm:P4_has_time_span><crm:E52_Time-span><crm:P78_is_identified_by>He was one of the nine saints who evangelized the Aksumite population in the 5th-6th century. He came to Ethiopia with his fellows during the reign of 
